                <text type="forecast">Sunny morning. Slight chance of a shower, most likely in the afternoon. Light winds becoming westerly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning then tending southwesterly during the afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to around 6 with daytime temperatures reaching around 19.</text>
